{"word":"ἀγρός","slug":"ἀγρός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγρός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>α</el> short by nature\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>ager, a field</el>, in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>fields, lands</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: in sg. <i>a farm</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>the country</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> the town, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>: <el>ἀγρῷ</el> or <el>ἐπ' ἀγροῦ</el> <i>in the country</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>κατ' ἀγρούς</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>ἐπ' ἀγρῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}